I don't get your reply Karadin.. All you did was back up what I had said. I didn't say anyone has actually carried out these actions but have implied it. Your above quote says you have made such implying remarks. /shrug. <br>
<br>
My only point is that regardless of any one persons morals, feelings or whatever there are only a few options to resolve this issue to take it from moral dilema to defined rule. <br>
<br>
What is present at this point is this moral issue.. If you team up to kill a flag mob you didn't deserve to get it and you are taking advantage of the spirit of the RTA. Not all agree with this, hence all the debate. The spirit of the RTA is talked about often yet it's not apparant. <br>
Either make the flag mobs rotation or open your minds and let the community decide which is best for THEM... not the RTA. <br>
<br>
If it were me.. I would let the &quot;spirit of the rathe&quot; determine what the &quot;spirit of the RTA&quot; is. Eq is about community.. not seperation. <br>
